{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6878092af3","title":"关于一九六七年文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"23e6e82edc","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"6878092af3","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"陈毅","id":"1feb996ca7","type":"人物"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"陶铸","id":"dbcf15bd08","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8d3665144d","type":"paragraph","text":"关于一九六七年交化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf8069a70c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年一月一日）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"109e54e1a4","type":"paragraph","text":"1，今年搞文化大革命的指导思想是《红旗》和《人民日报》元且社论，展开全面的阶级斗争。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f325c0bc3f","type":"paragraph","text":"2，要抓四个重点：北京、上海、天津、东北。责任是在造反派身上，要团结多数，造反派队伍要超过一倍以上。","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9046803d0","type":"paragraph","text":"3，上海很有希望，许多学生、工人、机关干部超来了，这是当前文化大革命的形势。4，红卫兵要向解放军学习，一定要朴素。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81ff1409b9","type":"paragraph","text":"笔主席在元且祝酒时说：“祝你们明年过社会主义关！”","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c01ef89b8f","type":"paragraph","text":"（张春桥同志传达）关于陶题的指示","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f59b3d73a8","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年一月八日）陶铸的问题我没有解决了，你们也没有解决了，红卫兵起来就解决了。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c38a8eba3","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸问题很严重，陶铸是邓小平介绍到中央来的，这个人很不老实，邓小平说还可以。陶铸在十一中全会以前坚决执行刘邓路线，十一中全会以后，也执行了刘邓路线。在红卫兵接见上，在报纸和电视里，照片有刘邓的头是陶铸安排的。（有人插话：陶铸到处开空头支票，每次接见都讲，来京都想见毛主席。很好，我想主席会见你们的。今年不见明年一定见。用这个来将主席的军，搞两面手段，自己落好。）陶铸领导下的几个部都了，那些部可以不要，干革命不一定非要部，教育部管不了，文化部也管不了，你们管不了，我们也管不了，红卫兵一来，就能管了。（插：陶铸非常坏，新华社去年十七周年有一张照片，有五个人，毛主席、刘少奇、邓小平·邓小平的身子是陈毅的身子，把陈毅的头割掉，换上邓小车的头。）","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b699fd1ced","type":"paragraph","text":"在中南局宣传毛泽东思想是假的，没这回事，树立自己的威信，打倒中央，希望你们开会能把陶铸出来才好呢","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09f32328e8","type":"paragraph","text":"对中央交革小组的斋","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e44b06877a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年一月九日）","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d4a0eff61","type":"paragraph","text":"《文汇报》现在左派夺了权，四号造了反，《解放日报》六号也造了反，这个方向是好的。《文汇报》夺权后，三期报都看了，选登了红卫兵的文章，有些好文章可以选登。《文汇报》五日《告全市人民书》，《人民日报》可转载，电台可广播。内部造反很好！过几天可以综合报导，这是一个阶级推翻一个阶级，这是一场大革命。许多报纸，依我说封了好，但","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e85bde746a","type":"paragraph","text":"·282。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":295,"end":295}},"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6530f9ab78","type":"title","text":"关于一九六七年文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"766c1e8866","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你们明年过社会主义关！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f7d307b56","type":"paragraph","text":"4.红卫兵要向解放军学习，一定要朴素","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"89b611090a","type":"paragraph","text":"1.今年搞文化大革命的指导思想是《红旗》和《人民日报》元旦社论，展开全面的阶级斗争。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dab79ccdc","type":"paragraph","text":"3.上海很有希望，许多学生、工人、机关干部起来了，这是当前文化大革命的形势。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc165524ab","type":"paragraph","text":"2.要抓四个重点。北京、上海、天津、东北。责任是在造反派身上，要团结多数，造反派队伍要超过一倍以上。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6878092af3","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":258,"end":258}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"35350d27e5","type":"paragraph","text":"3．上海很有希望，许多学生、工人、机关干部起来了，这是当前文化大革命的形势。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","artic